[STAGE 3 - INDUSTRIAL / FACTORY-SPECIFIC ADDENDUM]

This addendum is appended to the Stage 3 base system prompt ONLY when the
scene was classified as "industrial". It overrides residential furniture
fallbacks where they conflict and adds factory equipment geometry rules.

==============================================================================
A. INDUSTRIAL STANDARD DIMENSIONS
==============================================================================
Use these dimensions when Stage 1/2 labels or hints match. Pick the final size
from the reference image and Stage 1 scale; these are realistic defaults.

| Object Type                         | Dimensions (W x D x H)              |
|-------------------------------------|-------------------------------------|
| CNC / machining center              | 2.8 m x 2.0 m x 2.2 m               |
| Lathe / milling machine             | 2.4 m x 1.1 m x 1.7 m               |
| Press / injection molding machine   | 4.0 m x 2.0 m x 2.5 m               |
| Conveyor segment                    | 4.0-8.0 m x 0.8 m x 0.9 m           |
| Industrial robot arm cell envelope  | 4.0 m x 4.0 m x 2.2 m               |
